Customization
Update Company Information
Edit the content in:

src/pages/Index.tsx - Home page content
src/pages/Projects.tsx - Projects data
src/pages/Builder.tsx - Property listings
Change Colors
Update the Tailwind config or use the color classes:

Primary: blue-600
Secondary: gray-900
Accent: green-500
Add New Pages
Create a new component in src/pages/
Add the route in src/App.tsx
